    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Design competitions in which entry is restricted to a small number of participants specifically invited to offer solutions; usually for complex projects or projects for which particular technical expertise is required.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
